Harley Jo Skorpenske suffers from lupus and has a handicap permit . 
  She stopped at a CVS in Cleveland and a note was left on her car saying she should be 'ashamed' that she had no right to park in a disabled space . 
  Harley's mother Corinna took to Facebook to defend her daughter and her illness . 
  She hopes to find the writer of the note and educate him or her about 'ghost diseases' Harley was diagnosed with the disease aged 16 . 
 